{
  "texts": [
    "This task shows a simple 2D depiction of two agents in a grid environment (see Supplementary Fig. 6 for an example).",
    "On each time step, the agents can move up, down, left or right, or stay in place, but cannot move through walls or boxes.",
    "The red agent has the objective of reaching a star in ten time steps.",
    "If the agent runs out of time they fail.",
    "The blue agent has the objective of either helping or hindering the red agent by pushing or pulling boxes around."
  ]
}